**** MOTIVATED SELLERS ****** SELLER OFFERING $10,000 USE AS YOU CHOOSE CONCESSIONS 
(CLOSING COST OR 2/1 RATE BUY DOWN) HOME IS PRICED WELL BELOW MARKET VALUE!

Nestled in the charming Haymount neighborhood, this gem is priced below market value, presenting an excellent opportunity for growth.  This 2-bedroom home, with the potential for a 3rd bedroom, features an open living/dining concept, a modern galley kitchen with elegant granite countertops, providing both style and functionality. Ample cabinetry ensures storage for your culinary essentials.

Step onto the expansive deck, offering a private oasis for relaxation and entertainment, with the fenced-in yard . An unfinished bonus room allows for ample storage, along with a spacious shed for additional convenience.

Conveniently close to dining, shopping, and entertainment, and with a short commute to Fort Liberty! 

Perfect for  first-time homebuyer, downsizing, or seeking your first investment, don't miss this!
